title: Ed Schultz Show - July 01, 2008 (48kbs Audio).mp3
description:
Tuesday on The Ed Schultz Show!

Norman Goldman our Senior Legal Analyst joins the 2nd hour of Tuesday&#039;s show to discuss the case of Joe Horn in Texas who was cleared of shooting and killing 2 burglers from his neighbor&#039;s home.

Retired Gen. Wes Clark joins the 2nd hour of Tuesday&#039;s show to discuss his comments about Sen. John McCain.

Robert Greenwald of Brave New Films joins the 3rd hour of Tuesday&#039;s show to discuss his new video titled "Lieberman Must Go!"

Dan McAllister, Treasurer-Tax Collector for San Diego County joins the 3rd hour of Tuesday&#039;s show to discuss John McCain&#039;s overdue property tax.


Also try listening to Thom Hartmann,  Mike Malloy,  Randi Rhodes and Jeff Farias
